name: Ouyang Ziyu 欧阳子虞
description:
This is a model trained using pictures from the character "Ouyang Ziyu", from the Chinese drama "Nichang", played by Bi Wenjun.

All that is required is to include "photo of zwx ouyangziyu" and occasionally "long hair" in your positive prompt. Sometimes, you may need to specify "girl" or "women" in the negative prompt as well, SD is way too biased towards producing females if "long hair" is used.

This model was made using Dreambooth. This is a "raw" model, it has some imperfections, as such, you may want to merge it with other advanced models like Deliberate to get even better results.

This model may produce NSFW content even though it was not trained to do so, be careful if you don't want it. If not, I recommend using inpainting.

meta.prompt: center view, photo of zwx ouyangziyu, (((long hair))), (((extremely long shot))), ((standing)), masterpiece, (((best quality))), (((sharp focus))), ((inside a Chinese temple))
meta.negativePrompt: (((close-up))), short shot, ((subject out of frame)), bad quality, worst quality, ((blurry)), (((1girl))), (((female))), bad anatomy, wrong proportions, disfigured, deformed, distorted, (short hair)

meta.prompt: (((extremely long shot))), (((hip level shot))), three quarters view, photo of zwx ouyangziyu, (((best quality))), (((long hair))), ((inside a Chinese temple)), masterpiece, (((sharp focus)))
meta.negativePrompt: (((close-up))), short shot, ((subject out of frame)), bad quality, worst quality, ((blurry)), (((1girl))), (((female))), bad anatomy, wrong proportions, disfigured, deformed, distorted, (short hair)
